@node "Giftware" "About the giftware concept..."
@toc "Legal Stuff"

    The OLE System is released under the concept of Giftware.  In this version I
have used only PD libraries.  In future I'd like to use the @{" ZedRexx " link "Copyright" 0} or
something similar to improve the OLE GUI.  In this case the OLE System will
become a shareware product, at low cost.
@endnode

@node "Registration" "Not really a registration..."
