continued.  Because of this don't send me your money, I can't ensure you that
the OLE System will be completed.  See @{" TODO " link "TODO" 0} for more informations.

    Anyway, if you like the OLE System, let me know this.  Give me every kind of
advices, I need to know your impressions.
@endnode

